		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影使用手上的梦想一心，进行至多5段的普通攻击，第4段具有突进和收回两个过程；5段普攻依次造成<span color="#ffacff">33.3%,33.3%,<br/>33.3%,33.3%+16.6%,50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">离影较远时，影收起梦想一心迅速朝玩家冲击，并施放两段斩击，冲击造成<span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害，两段斩击分别造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%,<br/>66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于影身后时，影立即转身斩击，造成<span color="#ffacff">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影使用手上的梦想一心，进行至多3段的范围横劈攻击，3段普攻依次造成<span color="#ffacff">16.6%,<br/>16.6%,50%</span><span>伤害，</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="406" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影依次斩出3个雷轮，每个雷轮造成<span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害，最后水平劈出一道雷刃，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/影.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1268" y="619" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/影.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1248" y="598" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="417" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影作刀势，在场地上依次召唤1-3个闪烁的雷眼，接触造成4段<span color="#ffacff">5.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="421" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影用梦想一心画圈后将其举向天空，召唤9个雷球在场地边缘以顺时针顺序下落，雷球下落造成<span color="#ffacff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，留下雷痕持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">12.5%</span><span>伤害；雷球全落下后影在场地中间施放次元斩，造成4段</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，最后碎屏斩造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
