		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影进行旋斩、冲击、旋斩最多3段的普通攻击，3段攻击依次造成<span color="#ffacff">16.6%x2,<br/>16.6%,58.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
